divs: Sighting DetailsI was in eastvale California. I just got off work at 12:30. I clocked out walked outside heard the noise of a propeller plane and I looked up to see it. that's when I saw a jetlike craft all white with no decals, it had 4 wings that wings that were angled forward with rods protruding off the ends. I stopped in the middle of the parking lot and watched it go west for about 2 minutes and then it was gone.
